1) Reuse possibly left over material or broken material 
2) creates a custom look
3) doesn’t break the bank with this diy
.
Cons:
1) time consuming 
2) requires some concrete skill 
3) if not done correctly some of the tile edges can be sharp
.
Let me know what you think or if I missed anything. DIY or D-I-Why?

.

.

.
